body:
# The Silent Forest

Walking through the forest, he noticed how **silent** everything was. No birds. No insects. Not even the wind.

```javascript
// A simple test code block
function hello() {
  console.log("Hello, world!");
}
```

That’s when he realized the silence wasn’t natural—it was watching him.

### Key Takeaways
- Silence can be more terrifying than noise.
- Trust your instincts.
- Stories breathe life into plain text.
